
@startuml

' Define the classes
class Person {
  +personID: String
  +phone: String
  +keywords: List<String>
  +institutionCode: String
}

class Institution {
  +institutionCode: String
  +name: String
}

class Article {
  +doi: String
  +title: String
  +authors: List<Person>
  +authorPositions: List<Integer>
  +type: String (PeerReviewed / TechnicalReport)
}

class PeerReviewedArticle extends Article {
  +citationCount: Integer
  +reviewers: List<Person>
}

class TechnicalReport extends Article {
  +publisher: String
}

class Publisher {
  +name: String
  +journals: List<Journal>
}

class Journal {
  +name: String
  +impactFactor: Double
  +publisher: Publisher
}

' Relationships

' A person belongs to an institution
Person "1" --o "0..1" Institution : belongsTo

' A person can be an author of an article
Person "1" --o "0..*" Article : authoredBy

' A person can be a reviewer of a peer-reviewed article
Person "1" --o "0..*" PeerReviewedArticle : reviewedBy

' An article has authors and their positions
Article "1" --o "0..*" Person : author (with multiplicity)

' A peer-reviewed article has reviewers
PeerReviewedArticle "1" --o "0..*" Person : reviewer

' An article can be a technical report, which is published by an institution
TechnicalReport "1" --o "0..1" Institution : publishedBy

' A technical report is associated with a publisher
TechnicalReport "1" --o "0..1" Publisher : publishedBy

' A publisher has journals
Publisher "1" --o "0..*" Journal : hasJournals

' A journal is published by a publisher
Journal "1" --o "1" Publisher : publishedBy

@enduml

---

### Explanation of Key Relationships:

- **Person** is associated with an **Institution**.
- **Person** can be an **Author** of an **Article**.
- **Person** can be a **Reviewer** of a **PeerReviewedArticle**.
- **Article** has a list of **Authors** and their **author positions**.
- **PeerReviewedArticle** has **Reviewers**.
- **TechnicalReport** is published by an **Institution**.
- **TechnicalReport** is also associated with a **Publisher**.
- **Publisher** publishes **Journals**, each with a **name** and **impact factor**.
- **Journal** is published by a **Publisher**.
- **PeerReviewedArticle** is only published in **Journals**.

